Author: Idahurr
Text: Your body is still growing, you can afford to overeat on occasion :) Especially if you are already at a healthy or low weight, your body will thank you for the extra nutrition (even if you weren't eating *health* food exactly) if you have been staying under maintenance. Don't get too down!

Author: punk_wannabe
Text: darling, youre young and growing. i know it's much easier said than done, but try not to worry too much about the occasional day of eating above maintenance. you're not doing anything wrong.
